## Phase 2: Context Summary Presentation (AI Presents, Human Reviews)

After gathering is complete, AI **MUST** present a summary to the user in the following structured format:

```markdown
## Task Context Summary

### Task Understanding
> [Restate understanding of the task in one paragraph]

### Background Information
- [Key background extracted from docs/historical conversations, with doc links]

### Existing Design Decisions
| Document | Core Conclusion | Status |
|----------|-----------------|--------|
| [Doc Path] | [One-sentence conclusion] | [Completed/In Progress/Pending] |

### Code Dependencies
| Module | Path | Relationship |
|--------|------|--------------|
| [Module Name] | [File Path] | [Depends/Depended on/Needs Mod] |

### Existing Rules
- [Whether .mdc rules exist] → [If so, explain content]
- [Hook hit status] → [Whether plugin_hook was read and key fields hit]

### Historical Conversations
- [Conversation Title](Conversation UUID) - [Core content summary]

### Pending Confirmations
1. [Questions or assumptions requiring user confirmation]
```

