## Phase 3: Requirement Confirmation (Human Decision)

After presenting the summary, **wait for user confirmation**:

1. Whether task understanding is accurate
2. Clarify pending confirmations one by one
3. User decides the next direction

**AI only answers questions and provides information in this phase, and does not proactively advance.**

> **【Mandatory Design Review Reminder】**
> If the current task involves the following:
> - New database table creation, storage solutions, field design
> - Core component selection and configuration
> - New interface (API) design
> **AI MUST proactively remind the user in this phase**: "These design schemes need to follow existing specifications and **MUST pass a manual review before implementation can begin**. Please confirm if it has passed review, or if you need me to output a design document draft for review first?"

