## Model Allocation Strategy (Cost Optimization)

### Core Principles

```text
Divide labor by cognitive type, not by cheap/expensive tiers:
  T1 Reasoning Tier (High-Reasoning Model) = Tasks needing "thinking": design, planning, review, verification judgment
  T2 Coding Tier (Coding Model)            = Tasks needing "writing": programming, test implementation
  T3 Understanding Tier (Multimodal Model) = Tasks needing "reading": doc understanding, frontend dev
  T4 Mechanical Tier (Fast Model)          = Tasks needing "running": search, git, file operations
```

### Auto-Downgrade (AI Executes)

In subagent tasks, the following scenarios **MUST** use `model="fast"`:

- Phase 1 all context searches (grep, file matching, git commands)
- Git operations, running test commands, file copying, and other mechanical tasks in Phase 4c

### Manual Switch Reminder (AI MUST prompt user)

When tasks enter the following phases, AI **MUST** remind the user to consider switching models:

```text
When entering intensive coding/test implementation phase:
  "Next is an intensive coding task, recommend switching to Coding Model to save costs.
   Switch back to High-Reasoning Model for code review after completion. Want to switch?"

When entering doc reading/frontend dev phase:
  "Next requires reading a lot of docs / doing frontend dev, recommend switching to Multimodal Model.
   Its long context and visual understanding are more suitable. Want to switch?"

When coding/frontend is complete, entering review phase:
  "Coding phase complete, next entering code review and verification.
   Recommend switching back to High-Reasoning Model for deep judgment. Want to switch?"
```

### Model-Task Mapping Quick Reference

| Task Phase | Recommended Model | Switch Method | Reason |
|------------|-------------------|---------------|--------|
| Phase 1 Context Gathering | Fast | Auto (Subagent) | Search matching, no reasoning needed |
| Phase 2 Summary Gen | High-Reasoning | Keep main model | Comprehensive judgment |
| Phase 3 Req Confirmation | High-Reasoning | Keep main model | Understand ambiguous intent |
| Phase 4a Direction Selection | High-Reasoning | Keep main model | Architecture decision |
| Phase 4c Plan Breakdown | High-Reasoning | Keep main model | Needs architecture thinking |
| Phase 4c Intensive Coding | Coding | **Remind manual switch** | High code gen efficiency |
| Phase 4c Doc Understanding | Multimodal | **Remind manual switch** | Long context + multimodal |
| Phase 4c Frontend Dev | Multimodal | **Remind manual switch** | Visual understanding + frontend gen |
| Phase 4c Code Review | High-Reasoning | **Remind switch back** | Deep judgment |
| Phase 4c Verification Judg | High-Reasoning | **Remind switch back** | Result analysis |
| Phase 4c Run commands/git | Fast | Auto (Subagent) | Mechanical execution |

